===Championships and accomplishments===
*'''[[American Wrestling Association]]'''
**[[AWA World Tag Team Championship]] ([[AWA World Tag Team Championship#Title history|1 time]]) <U+2013> with [[Adrian Adonis]]<ref name=OWOW/><ref name=CageTitles>{{cite web|url=http://www.cagematch.de/?id=2&nr=53&view=erfolge#erfolge|title=Cagematch title listings}}</ref>

