**Iron Mike Mazurki Award ([[Cauliflower Alley Club#1999|1999]])

*'''[[Heart of America Sports Attractions|Central States Wrestling]]'''
**[[NWA World Tag Team Championship (Central States version)|NWA World Tag Team Championship ''(Central States version)'']] ([[NWA World Tag Team Championship (Central States version)#Title history|1 time]]) <U+2013> with Tank Patton<ref name=CageTitles/>

*'''[[Continental Wrestling Association]]'''
**[[Memphis Wrestling Southern Heavyweight Championship|AWA Southern Heavyweight Championship]] ([[Memphis Wrestling Southern Heavyweight Championship#Title history|2 times]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wrestling-titles.com/us/tn/cwa/awa-s-h.html|title=AWA Southern Heavyweight Championship history}}</ref>

*'''International Wrestling Institute and Museum'''
**[[Frank Gotch]] Award (2003)

*'''[[List of National Wrestling Alliance territories|NWA Mid-Pacific Promotions]]'''
**[[NWA Hawaii Tag Team Championship]] ([[NWA Hawaii Tag Team Championship#Title History|1 time]]) <U+2013> with Steve Strong<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wrestling-titles.com/us/hi/hi-t.html|title=NWA Hawaii Tag Team Championship history}}</ref>

*'''[[Pacific Northwest Wrestling]]'''
**[[NWA Pacific Northwest Heavyweight Championship]] ([[NWA Pacific Northwest Heavyweight Championship#Title History|2 times]])<ref name=OWOW/><ref name=CageTitles/>
**[[NWA Pacific Northwest Tag Team Championship]] ([[NWA Pacific Northwest Tag Team Championship#Title History|5 times]]) <U+2013> with Bull Ramos (2), [[Buddy Rose]] (2) and Jerry Oates (1)<ref name=OWOW/><ref name=CageTitles/>

*'''[[Pro Wrestling Illustrated]]'''
**PWI ranked him #'''239''' of the 500 best singles wrestlers during the "PWI Years" in 2003
**PWI ranked him #'''67''' of the 100 best tag teams of the "PWI Years" with [[Adrian Adonis]]

*'''[[World Wrestling Entertainment]]'''
**[[WWE Hall of Fame]] ([[WWE Hall of Fame#2004|Class of 2004]])<ref name=WWEProfile>{{cite web|url=http://www.wwe.com/superstars/halloffame/inductees/jesseventura/bio/|title=WWE profile}}</ref>

